Cng ng PITVN (Professional IT Vit Nam) h tr min ph cc vn v bn quyn Windows, Office, Antivirus, Software.
www.facebook.com/groups/pitvn
2
Microsoft Windows
3
* Ni quy PITVN (Regulations) Link
* ISO Windows & Server ly t knh MSDN v VLSC ca Microsoft.
*Ch l b iso ci t, cha c bn quyn, khuyn ngh chn ngy cp nht mi nht.
* Mt khu gii nn PITVNcommunity, mt khu c PITVN
* tm kim nhanh th nhn Ctrl+F, g t kha cn tm v d: ltsb.
* u tin chn Consumer v Pro cho windows. My cu hnh yu th nn chn ltsc (2019-2021-2024) cho ph hp.
* Khuyn ngh: My Intel gen10 tr xung nn ci win10. My gen 11 tr ln hy ci win11.
* Khi ci t xong Windows th bn ng bi ln PITVN c h tr kch hot hon ton min ph.
* SHA1 ly theo file iso, khng phi file nn, gii nn ri mi kim tra m SHA1.
* Cn kim tra m MD5/SHA1 khi ti v bo ton d liu: Xem hng dn
* Hng dn ci t windows li bng wintohdd m khng cn dng USB/DVD: Xem hng dn
* Sao lu bn quyn vnh vin sau khi c h tr kch hot: Xem hng dn
* Thm Drivers vo Windows ISO bng ng dng PowerISO: Xem hng dn
* To tp tin autounattend.xml nhm tr li sn cho cc thit lp ban u ca win10-11: Xem hng dn
* Tm kim Driver Intel RST VMD cho CPU gen 11-13: Xem hng dn
* Hng dn ci t windows bng a di ng (USB) qua ng dng Rufus: Xem hng dn
* Hng dn ti Windows 10-11 ISO mi nht t chnh hng Microsoft bng ng dng Fido: Xem hng dn
